 {"id":"frankenjax-5nc","title":"Add integration tests validating no not-yet-implemented strings remain in error paths","description":"CONTEXT: After all stub resolutions, this test prevents regressions by asserting that banned substrings never appear in any error message across the entire primitive x dtype matrix.\n\nSCOPE: Create a new test file crates/fj-conformance/tests/no_stub_regression.rs that:\n  1. EVAL SWEEP: For every Primitive variant (110 total), attempt eval_primitive with representative inputs for each dtype (I64, U32, U64, F64, Complex128, Bool). Collect errors. Assert no error .to_string() contains: not yet implemented, not yet supported, Default placeholder, or stub/placeholder/mock.\n  2. EGRAPH SWEEP: For every Primitive variant, attempt jaxpr_to_egraph lowering. For errors, verify message says unsupported or excluded (not not yet supported).\n  3. DISPLAY SWEEP: Construct every EvalError and EGraphLoweringError variant, call .to_string(), verify none contain banned substrings.\n  4. LOGGING: Print a summary table at the end: primitive | dtype | result (ok/error) | error_msg_snippet. Use --nocapture to see.\n\nDEPENDS ON: All other tasks in the epic: frankenjax-5a3 (complex binary), frankenjax-hdk (complex unary), frankenjax-cmb (complex select/clamp), frankenjax-znf (egraph categorization), frankenjax-fad (fuzzer).\n\nTESTING: This IS the test. Run with cargo test -p fj-conformance --test no_stub_regression -- --nocapture.\n\nACCEPTANCE: Test passes with zero banned-substring matches across all 110 primitives x 6 dtypes = 660 combinations, plus all egraph lowering paths, plus all error Display strings.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-02T23:27:23.444655514Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-03T02:25:01.119992764Z","closed_at":"2026-04-03T02:25:01.119743612Z","close_reason":"Added no-stub regression integration coverage across all primitives and representative dtypes, plus egraph/error-display sweeps; verified with rch cargo test -p fj-conformance --test no_stub_regression -- --nocapture and workspace check/clippy/fmt","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"frankenjax-5nc","depends_on_id":"frankenjax-5a3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-03T00:22:50.853988472Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"frankenjax-5nc","depends_on_id":"frankenjax-cmb","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-03T00:22:51.096324101Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"frankenjax-5nc","depends_on_id":"frankenjax-fad","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-02T23:27:32.932438792Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"frankenjax-5nc","depends_on_id":"frankenjax-hdk","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-03T00:22:50.974190463Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"frankenjax-5nc","depends_on_id":"frankenjax-znf","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-02T23:27:32.851649317Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
